subject: ANN: Still time to join Exploring Programmer Tests workshop at XP/Agile Universe 2003!
msgSnippet: Everyone: There is still time to join the workshop Exploring Programmer Tests at this year s XP/Agile Universe 2003 conference, running August 10-13, in New
messageBody:
Everyone:

There is still time to join the workshop "Exploring Programmer Tests" at
this year's XP/Agile Universe 2003 conference, running August 10-13, in New
Orleans, LA.

To join the workshop, please register at the conference web site
(http://www.xpuniverse.com), then proceed to the workshop web site
(http://diasparsoftware.gotdns.com:762) to submit your position paper. We
will accept submissions until August 10 or space runs out!

If you have any questions, do not hesitate to contact me at
<jbr@...>

Thanks, and we hope to see you there!

[We apologize if you receive this more than once.]
